  "narrative": {
    "text": "Korea, Republic of is a East Asia and Pacific country with a DB-type pension system centred on the National Pension Service (NPS) \u2013 Earnings-Related DB. The system includes 2 schemes: National Pension Service (NPS) \u2013 Earnings-Related DB, Basic Pension (\uae30\ucd08\uc5f0\uae08) \u2013 Means-Tested. The normal retirement age is 63 for both men and women. Contributions total 9.0% of insurable earnings (4.5% employee, 4.5% employer).",
